How to use videoObject;
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
int takePicture() - This will grab a frame from the video device.

int returnColorDepth() - This will return what colordepth the picture is at.

int returnPictureSize() - This will return Width * Height;

int returnPictureWidth() - This will return Width;

int returnPictureHeight() - This will return Height;

int returnPicturePalette() - This will return the type of Palette;

unsigned char* dumpPicture() - This will return the picture taken with takePicture();

rgbColor returnNextRGB() - The first time this is called it will return the pixel's rgb value at location 1, the next time it is called it will return the value at location 2 .. etc.


